Package: shinyExametrika
Title: A Shiny GUI for the exametrika Psychometric Package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Koji",
           family = "Kosugi",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kosugitti@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9014-738X"))
Description: Provides a web-based graphical user interface for the exametrika
    psychometric analysis package. Supports Classical Test Theory (CTT),
    Item Response Theory (IRT), Latent Class Analysis (LCA), Latent Rank
    Analysis (LRA), Biclustering, and more, with bilingual (English/Japanese)
    interface.
